Feature: agent-vault is the sole credential surface under fabro and the native secret store holds only placeholders

  Agent-vault-only credential injection — ADR-049 (agent-vault is the SOLE credential surface
  under fabro; fabro's native secret system is a FORBIDDEN surface), Anchored on ADR-048.
  Formalizes hard-invariant #2 (David-explicit). Evidence: findings/fabro-spike/
  03-fabro-launch.md (+03a/03b/03c, the U5 credential shim), 04-goal-demo.md section 3
  invariant #2, and 05-structural-loop.md section 3.2 (HELD/verified every run). The fabro
  native vault holds only __PLACEHOLDER__ for GITHUB_TOKEN and ANTHROPIC_API_KEY; nothing
  real is ever written to or read from it. Real LLM traffic sends a dummy x-api-key to the
  in-container anthropic-oauth-shim (~180-line stdlib bridging fabro's x-api-key adapter to
  the fleet OAuth Bearer), then via container HTTPS_PROXY to agent-vault (real OAuth) to a
  200 — the shim resolving the last load-bearing x-api-key-vs-OAuth-Bearer blocker. This is a
  LEAD-PROCESS contract pin with no current BC addressee; NOT dispatchable via assign_scenarios,
  flagged for the discriminator should a fabro-orchestration BC be created. Distinct from
  features/launcher-credentials and features/bc-launcher 45 (claude-oauth-brokered) / 50
  (no-real-credential-observable): this pins fabro-native-secrets-FORBIDDEN plus the
  x-api-key-to-OAuth shim bridge; it does NOT duplicate 45/46/50.
  @scenario_hash:9c7b4e8280665239
  Scenario: a dummy x-api-key request reaches a real OAuth 200 via the shim and agent-vault while the fabro secret store holds only placeholders
    Given a fabro native vault holding only __PLACEHOLDER__ for GITHUB_TOKEN and ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
    And an in-container anthropic-oauth-shim reachable via the container HTTPS_PROXY to agent-vault
    When an in-container agent issues an LLM request bearing a dummy x-api-key
    Then the request flows through the anthropic-oauth-shim, then HTTPS_PROXY, then agent-vault, and returns a real OAuth 200
    And the real credential appears only on the wire and never in the fabro native secret store
